Now, what about when we input
4 into the function?

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:29.720
Let me do this in magenta.

00:01:29.720 --> 00:01:32.440
So what happens if I input
4 into my function?

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:34.390
So this is 4 right here.

00:01:34.390 --> 00:01:38.120
Well, according to these points,
there's two points

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:41.440
that relate to 4 that
4 can be mapped to.

00:01:41.440 --> 00:01:46.900
I could map it to the
point 4 comma 5.

00:01:46.900 --> 00:01:49.720
